Package ohos.data.search.schema

Class AppItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.data.search.model.IndexData
      • ohos.data.search.schema.Schema<AppItem>
        • ohos.data.search.schema.AppItem

  • public final class AppItem
extends Schema<AppItem>
    Represents the index schema for application items.

    This schema is used to create indexes for application items. It supports index fields appCategory, size, comment, downloadCount, rating, and all the fields in CommonItem. Among these fields, identifier is mandatory and can be set via the CommonItem#setIdentifier(String) method.

    Since:
    5
    SystemCapability
    SystemCapability.Data#DATA_SEARCH
